{"type": "article", "id": 39904, "title": "Prada 门店升级，以及，KITH 与 adidas 联名发布粉色 UltraBOOST | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-04-18T03:06:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 991, "name": "New Balance"}, {"id": 1038, "name": "Flyknit"}, {"id": 1066, "name": "Calvin Klein"}, {"id": 17255, "name": "KITH"}, {"id": 1653, "name": "Michael Kors"}, {"id": 39595, "name": "王府井"}, {"id": 4999, "name": "三宅一生"}, {"id": 11092, "name": "村上隆"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170418094140lFnd2LoOgxKVPDZi.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2017-04-17/doc-ifyeimzx6649869.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>王府井推出自有文创品牌</strong></a> | 日前，王府井百货集团宣布推出自有品牌“王府井梦工厂”，走民宿工匠路径，以创意产品集合店的形式进驻北京市百货大楼。 </p><p><a href=\"https://www.streetinsider.com/Corporate+News/Michael+Kors+%28KORS%29+Appoints+Thomas+J.+Edwards%2C+Jr.+as+CFO%2C+COO+and+Treasurer%3B+Joseph+Parsons+to+Retire/12783498.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Michael Kors 任命新的财务总监</strong></a> | Thomas Edwards 将接任 Joseph B.Parsons，成为 MK 的新的财务总监、执行副总裁、首席运营官，该任命立即生效。此前， Joseph B.Parsons 曾为 MK 工作超过 13 年。Thomas Edwards 曾为 Brinker 国际工作，拥有丰富的金融和运营经验。</p><p><a href=\"http://eprretailnews.com/2017/04/16/prada-stores-in-porto-cervo-present-new-store-image-710649/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>为吸引新一代年轻消费者，Prada 进行门店升级</strong></a> | 日前，Prada 揭幕了它在意大利&nbsp;Porto Cervo 的新店。设计和之前开的加勒比海店类似，融入了更多当地特色风格，除了成衣、配饰还有一些当地限定商品。该品牌表示 2017 年会改装 50 家门店，以吸引新一代消费者。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104452opVJsujfxLY9G1Fl.png\" data-ratio=\"0.723493\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><b><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/4/nike-lunarepic-flyknit-oreo-black-white\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nike 的革新跑鞋 LunarEpic Flyknit 推出奥利奥配色版本</a>。</b>这双鞋的筒袜套式鞋身由黑、白二色的 Flyknit 材质交织而成，黑色的 Swoosh 与 Flywire 飞线做装饰，并搭载带有激光切割和泡棉活塞的 Lunarlon 缓震大底，定价为 1399 元，现已发售。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104928bavDWnosCLA42P1c.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104936i3MKutJrhoHRjwIn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104936zsWd31FMrpfgmTQK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704181049367gZ6Js4cPXMIpfO0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104940uM2fmpFHPeycrq78.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><b>三宅一生发布 2017 秋冬系列</b>，主题为“Chromatic Fantasia 极光幻想曲”。该系列灵感来源于极光那如同幻象似的风景，各式各样的布料和色彩组合而成的服装穿戴在身上，从不同的角度会看到不一样的变化。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104901oGskTwCUp4fOc28H.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104836vQ76K5UXD9qnrIkx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104835QViBkqfndm57uTJZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104839230Y46PAWENgav7h.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704181048427GVmQDnSg9PKOBeh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704181048426P0BKUVi8XSwjJgs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104844PSstgz7R0fDqhVvF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104846zyujvU0qFGEaKgck.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104846SEks0dNbiZMujy69.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104900qPuWUxBkI5Gc7oEg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104901yh7Y2SXTLIFQPeog.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104900HSnsZe12dEtqIkcD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.378531\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/04/17/takashi-murakami-octopus-eats-its-own-leg-preview/\" rel=\"nofollow\">5 月 30 日，<b>日本艺术家村上隆的新作《章鱼吃掉自己的腿》即将发售</b></a>。这本书记录了村上隆的职业生涯中的作品和展览，探讨了他对于东方与西方、商业与艺术、古代与现代的看法。这本书共有 288 页，含有 250 张彩色照片，售价为 65 美元。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104614qGhbR7wDilt9NYzm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704181046249bn4u8sCY01eGWlk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104624lVn2M8m4pCdiI7A5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104624pYfCcozEsPhyWF3R.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.772947\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104632O1ChU3kDB2oLwYsZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/4/kith-adidas-ace-16-purecontrol-ultraboost-more-details-leak\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>KITH 与 adidas 联名的 ACE 16+ PureControl UltraBOOST 鞋款正式曝光</b></a>。这双鞋的鞋身是粉色调的无鞋带袜套 Primeknit ，两侧的阔面反光三线与白色支架呼应，搭载白色 BOOST 中底和橡胶外底。这双鞋还配备了定制的粉色鞋盒和鞋拔，将于 5 月 19 日正式发售，全球限量 500 双。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104649N3kBTmw7PCjvGKo1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104641P1SkBzTcbYOGJZhN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704181046419JNYuFIHPnvx1M7h.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104641UK581djyqzlWoiPO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704181046535PGYV9T1oSxEZ2uR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/4/calvin-klein-denim-logo-cap-true-icon-2017-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Calvin Klein 在它的 2017 春夏系列中，带来了一系列丹宁帽款设计</b></a>。该系列共有两款颜色，皆以可调节麂皮尾扣搭配前部的皮革标签共同呈现，售价为 40 欧元。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104716ZszwrjhEA9cBx5Yg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104707ZfaX6RqPzGH8ot34.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104707USTrEtgCA1ZBRaNh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104727ztXL3FgnYrbeNUl4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104716q3HcKdw8ATxUsjVO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104707qYrK40x8TpGCVAlO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/4/new-balance-247-breathe\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>New Balance 247 鞋款带来全新的 Breathe 系列</b></a>。该系列以轻薄透气的网眼与贴合舒适的氯丁橡胶结合构成鞋身，在两侧拼入皮革提高整体质感，搭载上 REVlite 缓震中底，共有三款配色。将于 5 月 1 日开始登陆各大指定店铺，售价为 10800 日元。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104746pwybYLF9gXuJi547.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104757ZjMlTXKheV1q5CAr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104757uDlmHN29StMFwbU0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104804IXV7KWQRSdjUMmlG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704181047562qBkF6ZwN81mHeoG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665657\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170418104757q8WlJS4Uy7eP2IOv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665657\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704181048045LQdzo3EuhBiwnba.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665657\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/04/17/takashi-murakami-octopus-eats-its-own-leg-preview/\" rel=\"nofollow\">highsnobiety</a></p>"}